Dialogue: 1,0:00:05.86,0:00:08.12,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\3c&121B70\4c&121B70}这里是哪里
Dialogue: 1,0:00:08.53,0:00:09.99,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\3c&121B70\4c&121B70}后来究竟发生了什么
Dialogue: 1,0:00:10.78,0:00:12.33,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\3c&0D1554\4c&0D1554}我这是死了吗
Dialogue: 1,0:00:25.17,0:00:26.84,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\3c&0D1554\4c&0D1554}这里是现实吗
Dialogue: 1,0:00:28.26,0:00:29.89,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\3c&0D1554\4c&0D1554}莫非是地狱
Dialogue: 1,0:00:43.82,0:00:45.49,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,请努力想象
Dialogue: 1,0:00:46.15,0:00:48.28,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,你将脱离肉体的束缚
Dialogue: 1,0:00:48.82,0:00:50.70,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,以出窍之魂体
Dialogue: 1,0:00:50.70,0:00:52.28,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,进入久堂的精神世界
Dialogue: 1,0:00:52.83,0:00:55.70,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,你要在那里找出他的灵魂
Dialogue: 1,0:00:56.46,0:00:57.29,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 1,0:00:57.58,0:01:00.08,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,美世小姐，请一定多多保重
Dialogue: 1,0:01:00.08,0:01:00.88,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,美世
Dialogue: 1,0:01:01.38,0:01:02.92,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,你一定能做到
Dialogue: 1,0:01:03.46,0:01:04.42,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,美世小姐
Dialogue: 1,0:01:05.01,0:01:06.17,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,美世小姐
Dialogue: 1,0:01:08.01,0:01:09.47,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,你是无可替代的人
Dialogue: 1,0:01:09.93,0:01:11.76,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,大家都相信着你
Dialogue: 1,0:01:12.51,0:01:13.68,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,准备好了吗
Dialogue: 1,0:01:14.89,0:01:15.39,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,好了
Dialogue: 1,0:01:18.31,0:01:20.02,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,我一定会回来的
Dialogue: 1,0:01:20.02,0:01:21.69,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,和老爷一起回来
Dialogue: 1,0:01:22.61,0:01:23.57,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,我出发了
Dialogue: 1,0:01:50.72,0:01:53.64,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,2026)\3a&aa}老爷
Dialogue: 1,0:02:04.73,0:02:06.23,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\3c&1A1C10\4c&1A1C10}这里是…
Dialogue: 1,0:02:06.73,0:02:08.49,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\3c&1A1C10\4c&1A1C10}斋森家…
Dialogue: 1,0:02:36.10,0:02:39.06,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\3c&0E0E23\4c&0E0E23}已经消灭的异形不断袭来
Dialogue: 1,0:02:39.56,0:02:42.43,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\3c&0E0E23\4c&0E0E23}却不见五道他们的人影
Dialogue: 1,0:02:42.81,0:02:46.52,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1160,1004)\3c&0E0E23\4c&0E0E23}这个世界果然不是现世吗
Dialogue: 1,0:02:47.48,0:02:50.36,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\3c&0E0E23\4c&0E0E23}但是，不管这里是哪里
Dialogue: 1,0:02:50.36,0:02:51.07,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\3c&0E0E23\4c&0E0E23}我都不能死在这种地方
Dialogue: 1,0:02:51.07,0:02:52.70,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\3c&325E80\4c&325E80\3a&66}我都不能死在这种地方
Dialogue: 1,0:02:53.24,0:02:54.45,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\3c&325E80\4c&325E80\3a&66}老爷
Dialogue: 1,0:02:55.82,0:02:56.33,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\3c&0E0E23\4c&0E0E23}美世
Dialogue: 1,0:02:57.99,0:02:59.95,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\3c&0E0E23\4c&0E0E23}美世，你在哪里
Dialogue: 1,0:03:00.33,0:03:02.29,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\3c&101D38\4c&101D38}在的话就答应一声
Dialogue: 1,0:03:02.29,0:03:03.33,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\3c&101D38\4c&101D38}美世
Dialogue: 1,0:03:19.47,0:03:21.22,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\3c&1C1611\4c&1C1611}老爷究竟在哪里
Dialogue: 1,0:03:25.19,0:03:25.85,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\3c&1C1611\4c&1C1611}是谁
Dialogue: 1,0:03:26.61,0:03:27.69,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,有人在吗
Dialogue: 1,0:03:28.57,0:03:29.40,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,来呀
Dialogue: 1,0:03:32.03,0:03:33.24,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\3c&272C13\4c&272C13\3a&66}等一下
Dialogue: 1,0:03:39.45,0:03:40.58,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 1,0:03:41.37,0:03:43.08,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,我在这里
Dialogue: 1,0:03:46.17,0:03:47.67,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\3c&272C13\4c&272C13\3a&66}等…等等
Dialogue: 1,0:04:03.68,0:04:05.02,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\3c&1C1611\4c&1C1611}你是…
Dialogue: 1,0:04:05.02,0:04:06.98,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\3c&1C1611\4c&1C1611}快来抓我呀
Dialogue: 1,0:04:13.03,0:04:14.90,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\3c&33381F\4c&33381F}这是什么
Dialogue: 1,0:04:17.11,0:04:19.83,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\3c&33381F\4c&33381F}在这里哦
Dialogue: 1,0:04:24.58,0:04:26.96,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord0\shad0}我要尽快找到老爷
Dialogue: 1,0:04:39.89,0:04:41.22,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\3c&0F1870\4c&0F1870}这扇门…
Dialogue: 1,0:04:42.64,0:04:44.68,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\3c&0F1870\4c&0F1870}我认识
Dialogue: 1,0:05:10.29,0:05:11.71,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\3c&0F1870\4c&0F1870}你是…
Dialogue: 1,0:05:14.55,0:05:15.51,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord0\shad0}我自己?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:39.86,0:05:40.57,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord0\shad0}美世
Dialogue: 1,0:05:43.41,0:05:45.58,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\3c&313D70\4c&313D70\3a&66}我要去找美世
Dialogue: 1,0:05:55.42,0:05:57.26,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\3c&313D70\4c&313D70}本来要去接美世
Dialogue: 1,0:05:57.80,0:05:58.84,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\3c&313D70\4c&313D70}却被困在了这里
Dialogue: 1,0:06:00.22,0:06:02.05,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,我要再见她一面
Dialogue: 1,0:06:02.34,0:06:03.30,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,我要向她道歉
Dialogue: 1,0:06:03.30,0:06:03.51,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\3c&0C0A0C\4c&0C0A0C\3a&aa}我要向她道歉
Dialogue: 1,0:06:04.60,0:06:05.93,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord0\shad0}可是
Dialogue: 1,0:06:06.10,0:06:07.02,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\3c&0F0E33\4c&0F0E33}我去得了吗
Dialogue: 1,0:06:07.89,0:06:09.85,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\3c&0F0E33\4c&0F0E33}不对，我必须去
Dialogue: 1,0:06:11.43,0:06:13.81,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\3c&0F0E33\4c&0F0E33}我还不能…
Dialogue: 1,0:06:14.23,0:06:16.56,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\3a&88\3c&0F0E33\4c&0F0E33}倒在这种地方
Dialogue: 1,0:06:17.61,0:06:20.07,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\3c&0F0E33\4c&0F0E33}你究竟是…
Dialogue: 1,0:06:20.82,0:06:23.32,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\3c&09050E\4c&09050E\3a&88}你不能见老爷
Dialogue: 1,0:06:23.53,0:06:24.49,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\3c&09050E\4c&09050E}为什么
Dialogue: 1,0:06:24.91,0:06:28.33,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\3c&09050E\4c&09050E}因为你配不上老爷
Dialogue: 1,0:06:29.20,0:06:31.16,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\3c&08091C\4c&08091C}你一直孤身一人
Dialogue: 1,0:06:31.16,0:06:32.71,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\3c&08091C\4c&08091C}今后也一样
Dialogue: 1,0:06:32.96,0:06:35.58,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\3c&08091C\4c&08091C}毕竟那样比较轻松
Dialogue: 1,0:06:36.17,0:06:38.09,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\3c&040430\4c&040430}你一直孤独地活着
Dialogue: 1,0:06:39.46,0:06:42.38,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\3c&040430\4c&040430}其实你心里很清楚吧
Dialogue: 1,0:06:43.47,0:06:46.89,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\3c&040430\4c&040430}你辜负了老爷对你的善意
Dialogue: 1,0:06:48.10,0:06:48.97,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\3c&040430\4c&040430}甚至伤害了他
Dialogue: 1,0:06:48.97,0:06:50.18,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\3c&232754\4c&232754}甚至伤害了他
Dialogue: 1,0:06:51.39,0:06:52.64,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\3c&232754\4c&232754}你这种做法
Dialogue: 1,0:06:53.19,0:06:56.44,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\3c&232754\4c&232754}害得老爷仍在生死边缘挣扎
Dialogue: 1,0:06:57.36,0:06:59.23,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\3c&232754\4c&232754}和你有牵扯的人
Dialogue: 1,0:06:59.53,0:07:01.40,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\3c&232754\4c&232754}都会变得不幸
Dialogue: 1,0:07:03.15,0:07:04.36,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\3c&232754\4c&232754}所以你不应该
Dialogue: 1,0:07:04.99,0:07:07.37,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\3c&232754\4c&232754}待在老爷身边
Dialogue: 1,0:07:08.62,0:07:10.25,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\3c&232754\4c&232754}或许如此吧
Dialogue: 1,0:07:11.20,0:07:13.00,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\3c&232754\4c&232754}我觉得自己一无是处
Dialogue: 1,0:07:13.71,0:07:17.38,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\3c&232754\4c&232754}所以一直想要改变自己
Dialogue: 1,0:07:17.96,0:07:19.92,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\3c&060513\4c&060513}或许你说得没错
Dialogue: 1,0:07:20.63,0:07:23.17,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\3c&060513\4c&060513}我不应该待在老爷身边
Dialogue: 1,0:07:23.80,0:07:26.38,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\3c&060513\4c&060513}我也是这么想的
Dialogue: 1,0:07:27.30,0:07:28.10,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\3c&060513\4c&060513}但是…
Dialogue: 1,0:07:29.51,0:07:30.85,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\3c&17112F\4c&17112F}现在不同了
Dialogue: 1,0:07:30.85,0:07:32.77,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\3c&17112F\4c&17112F}因为得到了异能吗
Dialogue: 1,0:07:32.77,0:07:34.89,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\3c&17112F\4c&17112F}和异能没有关系
Dialogue: 1,0:07:36.02,0:07:40.40,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\3a&55\3c&060513\4c&060513}因为有许多人愿意为我着想
Dialogue: 1,0:07:40.98,0:07:46.82,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\3c&121540\4c&121540}让我觉得自己有资格待在老爷身边
Dialogue: 1,0:07:46.99,0:07:48.24,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\3c&121540\4c&121540}别撒谎了
Dialogue: 1,0:07:48.66,0:07:51.70,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\3c&121540\4c&121540}你一直觉得一个人比较轻松
Dialogue: 1,0:07:51.70,0:07:52.87,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\3c&121540\4c&121540}不是吗
Dialogue: 1,0:07:52.87,0:07:55.04,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\3c&121540\4c&121540}不，不是那样的
Dialogue: 1,0:07:55.25,0:07:56.41,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\3c&121540\4c&121540}别自欺欺人
Dialogue: 1,0:08:01.63,0:08:03.34,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\3c&121540\4c&121540}自从母亲去世后
Dialogue: 1,0:08:03.97,0:08:06.34,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\3c&121540\4c&121540}你每天都过着地狱般的生活
Dialogue: 1,0:08:07.14,0:08:11.18,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\3c&121540\4c&121540}所以在不知不觉中麻痹了自己
Dialogue: 1,0:08:12.18,0:08:13.47,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\3c&121540\4c&121540}因为不这样
Dialogue: 1,0:08:13.47,0:08:15.89,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\3c&121540\4c&121540}你就活不下去
Dialogue: 1,0:08:18.10,0:08:22.40,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\3c&121540\4c&121540}我确实以为，自己会那样活一辈子
Dialogue: 1,0:08:23.15,0:08:23.65,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\pos(625.143,1004)\3c&121540\4c&121540}可是…
Dialogue: 1,0:08:24.90,0:08:27.24,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\pos(578.286,1004)\3c&121540\4c&121540}我相信自己能做出改变
Dialogue: 1,0:08:27.57,0:08:29.37,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\3c&121540\4c&121540}为时已晚
Dialogue: 1,0:08:29.37,0:08:32.24,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\3c&121540\4c&121540}你不是早就习惯放弃了吗
