Dialogue: 1,0:08:36.29,0:08:38.58,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\3c&121540\4c&121540}我已经不想再放弃了
Dialogue: 1,0:08:38.58,0:08:39.63,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\3c&121540\4c&121540}不可能
Dialogue: 1,0:08:39.63,0:08:40.62,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\3c&121540\4c&121540}怎么不可能
Dialogue: 1,0:08:40.62,0:08:41.50,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\3c&121540\4c&121540}就是不可能
Dialogue: 1,0:08:42.09,0:08:44.09,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\3c&121540\4c&121540}因为选择放弃很简单
Dialogue: 1,0:08:44.55,0:08:46.26,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\3c&121540\4c&121540}自己也不会受伤
Dialogue: 1,0:08:46.76,0:08:48.59,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\3c&121540\4c&121540}你就是这样的人
